<A>__{claire sleeps against the wall as a dog sniffs and licks her face. she awakens with a start the dog scurries away. claire rises and looks around. a local woman pushes a cart carrying the wrapped body of her husband through the otherwise quiet streets of managua. claire moves through the camp just coming to life, and looks around trying to interpret the eerie silence. a woman tends to her two small children.}
