<P>__{(it is good.)}
<A>__{the woman continues with her children, her comment unemotional, and claire smiles slightly and walks away, through a city awakening slowly to its victory. claire stops a red cross truck and shows the driver her picture of price. the picture means nothing to the driver. claire continues through the city, looking for price.}
